Receiving Officer, Johnson 6th Ark
18th August 1841
Received from Charles Buck Johnson of Scott County Ark Ninety seven dollars and seventy six cents which will be applied to the Purchase of the North half of unclear in Township four North of Range Thirty three west unclear  Seventy Eight acres and unclear hundredths.
unclear Receiver
unclear Johnson 6th Ark

We have this day sold unto Charles B Johnson of Fort Smith Arkansas the following lots viz lots No. 2 & 11 Block 3 laying on and fronting on the river to be more fully described in deeds to be made at some future time for the Consideration of three hundred & fifty dollars in six months from date of this sale. Fort Smith Oct 4th ...
... L. Mitchell
